html
 head
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    title Simple Dropbox
    style.
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        padding: 20px 250px;
      }
      li {
        font-size: 20px;
        padding: 10px 5px
      }
body
    | 
    h1 Nathan's Dropbox
    form(
      ref="uploadForm"
      id="uploadForm"
      action="http://localhost:8080/upload"
      method="post"
      enctype="multipart/form-data")
      <input type="file" name="uploadfile" />
      <input type="submit" value="Upload!" />
    | 
    h3 To Download: /download/:filename
    h3 Refresh to see cached files
    h3 Cached files:
    ul( id="filelist"
        style="list-style: none"
    )
      li= message0
      li= message1
      li= message2
      li= message3
      li= message4
    
    

